-have been tested with the PEC as part of their production process.
-Indeed the passport application pack was awarded the PEC Crystal Mark
-in autumn 2005. In addition IPS customer service staff have attended
-training courses run by the PEC to further improve the standards of
-communication with customers.</p><br>
