+and <i> (b)</i> a 999 call in each fire authority area.
+[89805]</p><p><a name="06101247002689"><b><a name="06101247004495">Angela
+E. Smith:</b> Fire and rescue authorities in England are
+required by the Fire and Rescue Service National Framework to have in
