+received from 136 of the 149 library authorities in England,
+representing a 91 per cent. response rate. These results, including
+projections for the whole sector, were published on 18
+September.</p><p><a name="06101247003780">The survey
+found that an estimated &#163;760 million is required to make all
+public libraries in England fit for purpose. Of this sum, &#163;130.8
