+impunity for those accused of human rights abuses in Darfur. In its
+Council Conclusions, it has regularly supported UN Security Council
+Resolution (UNSCR) 1593, which refers human rights abuses to the
+International Criminal Court (ICC). The EU calls on all parties in
+Sudan to co-operate fully with the
+ICC.</p><p><a name="06101265000674">In its latest
+Council Conclusions of 12 September, the EU condemns the continuing
+violations of the cease-fire by all parties, the violence directed at
+the civilian population and the targeting of humanitarian assistance.
