+from all violence and to guarantee respect for human rights. The
+Council endorses the statement by the UN Secretary-General to the UN
+Security Council on 11 September. In his statement he urges the
+Government of Sudan to embrace the spirit of UNSCR 1706 and warns that
+those who decide and carry out policies leading to death and suffering
+in Darfur will be held accountable.</p><br>
 
