-Communities and Local Government whether local authorities can require
-developers wishing to develop inside a special protection area (SPA)
-and its radius to provide land in mitigation for that development and
-its notional impact on the SPA.
-[87345]</p><p><a name="06101247003979"><b><a name="06101247004699">Yvette
-Cooper:</b> Development which has an adverse effect on the
-integrity of an SPA, and which is not directly connected with or
-necessary to the 
