+year, with the second meeting taking place in London in the
+spring.</p><p><a name="06101336004709">The forum,
+announced by my right hon. Friend the Prime Minister and President
+Chirac following the Franco-British summit on 9 June, is expected to
+attract considerable interest from both UK and French industry. It
+represents an excellent opportunity to develop civil nuclear
+cooperation between the two
+countries.</p><p><a name="06101336004710">Officials
+at the DTI and their counterparts at the Ministry of Finance and
+Industry in France are currently working together to develop important
